            <lg xml:id="TK86">
<l>celvirun tōmpi varuviruntu pārttiruppā</l>
<l>ṉalviruntu vāṉat tavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who, after looking after parting guests, looks to sit with coming guests,</l>
<l>shall be an honored guest to the celestials.</l>
